;/a&gt;：市场令人震惊，价格跌跌撞撞，然后惯常的闲聊者涌入。这有助于对&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/RwlQE_5qpG5szZpBZcg9WAJ4wUkD8_ghfxrVQW_-Ou5mYcgCyovveS_S6ImCKmQeiLn_JjE3ct6ULsN97hlAF8Rynm_quuS93aqgTS_DZZXwEnMn0LtIUrgBwiWN1j4upKZN0wpGtetolzw4HlexuowAk1MmR3ut0qSkzb5vH2WOddYCoAWGYY9S25uFg3rfRDVkLvvQn8ZGtgrpP-EAK6FdXR8ieAzrf35_zaooDI--QWkZu6mkMDQjZyXF1Iugbb5Bt_b5ZMYnBCA4pt4TIYQf9dMh9Y_I8JbwK0O1dFV1cWLEM4t95HBd06R6yFjHTKMg8X94OVrc2zgsy0BSchAIA4q_i-RJ30U858CHzq6OZsf1CXFrJOiQGS8/FyslBJBRmsxQvWhoJoacwHROhiCzmmKg/9" target="_blank"&gt;消费者情绪&lt;/a&gt;的非政府读物比估计的好，以及美国劳动部的第四个月份的通货膨胀数据。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 16px 0px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-radius: 8px; padding-bottom: 18px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/37-a9LpuAiDUCWuu5NShsZheYHXN3MQ83PxTD4MpX_jSWYyowVTrJ06N0BLOQM7pbnw9yqxhMk_a7g_RewHtFaEZOzinliJ5vo6oUjQgAoAxms13eW2AQAWA4nP3GedinIOkAOGku2oxbMJjUjTV4RAtpMGAdnoCDikYvdoxalJAfGZfFo9zND1ZOK_vM9IcviEDV4KSnH62rq-Bab0nXUG2WR5iV6at4UN1XJwFeQD56hFrXk1C4Do6j55yPyoGH4oL_TTAxkH1irsvk-iThctSuSAxmnnHEHVMobGAxPGU1j5YRwP7CuXxeYVN-8TELSK04udKZdUPe4PWmYf8DYQWGEnjaC61jxkS4y0eX7hhdgBpQkwCeepDA_o/Xa7Y7LM7T0ULGDShlOlAS_EkoSad6W1z/9" rel="nofollow" style="color: #000000; text-decoration: none; display: block;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i_Saf5TbctGQ/v0/550x381.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/t