 Trump）&lt;/strong&gt;至少目前有法庭&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;。&lt;/strong&gt;上诉法院裁定，总统可以&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/_cVKFTq-__cb14IFNwVBWLmf5OQmXC918YTK579hnYIiIQHjD7uIb__AXIII50kOttfo9hC9Tec96xGiXgxFYBLvsQAzGtDOBVOovvfkzJsLGWHHh17GPDB5X3InZRWWUTNECEiLTltf8u3OgDmuWNT_PTR6KjCHnV_nTmMr7l5BTEzQvdX-RxgFmu1FM_tZENy-8kDlsxNN_7cpB2_Wmo9f8b0N_BTNcnaAvsH9zf1KYRw4Zi8mbgyDaA3gO2OCpDu1dJiWV5xyxbKc8lg1vOFAZw/18br0rQWPQbY7i-IIAFE1RMXlWfxPlUm/9" target="_blank"&gt;继续&lt;/a&gt;使用&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/KnZ8Ea8KKfZbkjlzbeGtZh1vDXaiW8uRbzrFAU4JXso_CQljg6XHfTNYlDhrTTn37XrCmBHyIA_wAsyEtB_EpXgimFZuQkQct_O6ZQp-LmsJMThbzygnKslUfgryLjwWnpbT5mM23ViUTnXMYdrYYssGBR8HRfK9eX1gAEFhQ6bzAYmLyAhkszz710WYI_sLmdVlp4mpSCfe4e0gaRZEbkWFhUzsMh_pAvunRTk-IhJnACAx6rjyWwqka1AJx22RdmxyGngX1aLQZ1nssTBQRmRPIA/Z3sctzGAHLU22cHc0QSzUBqytuhK0Ivv/9" target="_blank"&gt;洛杉矶的部队&lt;/a&gt;来应对抗议活动。法院周二设定听证会，以进一步讨论。阅读我们的解释者，了解&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/XoghK9-G5plwKp9ta_6a4FvFfuUlUjb7adBuNhpXuH0yR48bNLxfeZd90x2a9AoY2c0sCS3GylPxr3ASizOYh3rNlCizxTLuHEgKZ9G_V9G-LT_G5TZrMceXvpHG0yaeCp0zabWqQnP-d-FdpCX2Lpd_Ce4qRDhVPQox5wRJHWQ2eA4bewJ12WqG9yHhjsTLL3dYj360km8O_6WDwZ7IJQ-u9pQNcR6Qy4VBNrH4Eshd8DH6RcpU7camesF7V1NQZRmAY3uIKwi4o1A20TqnfVdoBw/HRs2CedzNV71K_KVbhXUacrBxe1OIA5G/9" target="_blank"&gt;各个国家在抵抗特朗普方面拥有什么权力&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;在技​​术领域，&lt;/strong&gt; Meta &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7V4JGTF2LF4mqOnSIbsVUw7TQRyvuu8pahVVrHE2VuVS3Dojb-1jz0Yr_jzv_0M8b7am2J3gjOAXvscUeMTorugkPpwUspU3RO5qlSdNyM9njWnhy3UpPNwZFaPBru0fj2DV2QO7V9SgPVRoI0ynrVxotxvm6TDarHfGDSVsT9t4j_5-oHyogSQ5rejwEmKMXJxL7fcZ-vpyJ7W3VvnxwwoOsW2Dcm7SWv35OvkB4iT6-OGg4pZlWwB6HtmnXcXvONNfwpy40rT6sw10wu7g9CiCbA/HgDovUHoacykzuXe0L00l4dxTbLa6dXO/9" target="_blank"&gt;在AI规模上完成了数十亿美元的投资&lt;/a&gt;，并招募了这家初创企业的首席执行官加入其AI努力。马克·扎克伯格（Mark Zuckerberg）正在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/vlj0X3ENL00khqyApplPjVUNK6NEczE5g9oXNC6F9-0iun8Qw0iS5Mbwq2rPSScyb8lmTy_1hTExyvUlgHLCrNvOvsIV-VQxEOfz8WE2KqORYf623u85Nw7E5Gg8wguIF0zaKcGvgymzutRO32alrT0yL4F7wFMrGBpvoWsg3FtBxvtxgnmSNVpK7S6BoUInyX1X8nDvGHG4NvthSAMsEz_DDiv4tgbX9u2FrD4LGUpK8l-ThaCg23gs3dSPxrpt4e4eCV5peL-u2cQz5KKyzDYhDw/31r85E80S5y70ChCyaYOgMo-99mnS0Yl/9" target="_blank"&gt;组建一个专家团队&lt;/a&gt;，以实现人工智能，从&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/e122ChgNNwEldlK-YtB2rQeUaNlMh6pZn1gp0lDHFVmmhRqaRIRk6bymSOPIeksuV-rPCccWUprN-cp8cV77DhEBUfWxz1dn4ATIoDoCNHQrwuv4rqtiI2wO5KuxW-cz0p9sOhOcG7RIoImKIwEtmd0pOcyN8zmZ5DhdtXsEILanyh926MaWOixyg-HhUlC1wNWCKRA8rI3-s269Jws5JVZNmpBT6nZ0whPJHCIacm0WcD3z9W4zFLM4qoSAZl2u_qx1CCJDcjISGw_AGK_jtRdpOg/U5zeeUU7TMUOYq7ZA-FiyfV-fd1HfOv3/9" target="_blank"&gt;包括Google在内的&lt;/a&gt;多家技术公司&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/tNMHLoBR1h9r8_91KaMVhkIC8928wR1iaqg4U95yUOhLrnIbSB--yi20jGW465I5mtQMZfWQ0zb7AW73I8Jem-lMRJ-O7FW6r2fDiqRKqU1aPCZyOv6Auty3CE3wncPfRfVdqYSbcrQ3w3X-0LqGTyb3GcArgv56bb74WUKfKzgKXfjR8QxFcEiqaNXWQTB8nsvTQ_lM8Gq0wvbzpl30oS73o0132LdRFgaYjzT2ejMTVuoKKS-AnWRDeX_o3bsxxN5K8_grbJZ6Lo79xWyzF8Q-KA/L57UtfqFG2obUEwKMCOLBGp0SkhJVqN2/9" target="_blank"&gt;偷猎顶级工程师&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;座位11a的奇迹。&lt;/strong&gt; 40岁的英国公民Ramesh Vishwaskumar讲述了他是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/cd_beiwmd9PL_goi6TX6VGKTG0tw-XBY3s7DhCJHfaCmHwBUssFi06H4hMFUMqlAc7oBol78aTNuPsGODLClJonAO3ghVl33jctwYuBpngPZtk4SVRHrydEqyERE3a51XARjwvi4mXxOT9942ytdCLUrFHk096hlOceNhLmn3PihNk24jM2ckkTx5tv-nP9nXambxgbHlIAGy6VHjVylhUqX8hTJcqm59Xtf3Mu1pLFqlIianMtJTvoWXrCdzJeXuDV_uNd37QQbp4zzcxj6ia4Lyw/ZEGnRcqSiiH7Plr7A-EPp8u3mIUkXwvo/9" target="_blank"&gt;印度航空AI171航班的唯一幸存者&lt;/a&gt;的故事。他坐在第一行经济舱中，设法穿过飞机侧面破的门逃脱。十年来，这次坠机事故在最致命的航空事故中&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/bf4snV8w3TNvZHVr5MMhH7qYs